						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up out side the compound of the temple of Ellamma.</p>						

						<p>This is dated in cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Prajāpati, Āshāḍha, śu. 15, Thursday.</hi></p>						

						<p>It records the gift of land by certain individual (name not known), son of Pedi Tippinēni to the goddess Kalidēvamma. In characters of about the 17th-18th century A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
